@3wheelingtots yes can’t go wrong with them 😊😋👍🏻

In case you didn’t know, @songfabkt is now providing islandwide delivery!

Whatsapp +65 93836049 to order
• Minimum order of $30
• Flat delivery fee of $3
• Free delivery for orders $50 and above
• Order timing (limited slots available): 10am & 3pm
• Quote NEW10 to enjoy 10% off your first order
• Available on GrabFood too

Overall I was pleased with Song Fa Bak Kut Teh’s delivery service.

The food was delivered within the stated timeframe, and it was still warm upon arrival.

Best of all, there were plenty of soup base given so I could do my own soup top-ups!

The flat delivery fee of $3 is also the cheapest I’ve seen in Singapore so far.

Full review via link in bio.
